{"tid":1104163,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工返到冇咩人生真係好頹","createTime":"2019-04-13T02:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T05:54:31.000Z","uid":834,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bc73939de7da80d14bc7f10223f47d2f80c93f8a","tid":1104163,"uid":834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:44:20.000Z","msg":"本身唔係咩叻仔<br />\n白紙轉行做左差不多就黎一年 <br />\nD野都係未上到哂手<br />\n同埋而家做到個人好似七勞八傷咁<br />\n久唔久就病一兩日咁<br />\n又成日得閒就OT 放工唔想見人<br />\n放假都有時淨係想係屋企訓多D<br />\n連其他人都冇咩機會見到<br />\n<br />\n但係自己好似根本搵唔到D咩工去轉<br />\n裸辭又冇舊錢去保障自己同屋企既日子<br />\n好似唯有死死地氣去繼續做而家份工<br />\n<br />\n愈返工愈覺得自己因為依份工失去左/失去緊好多野<br />\n<br />\n如果係你地 又會點做?<br />\n繼續返而家份工頂住先, 慢慢騎牛搵馬?<br />\n屌佢老母 裸辭啦!?"},{"pid":"641867d8e8292de45474471ea62ddf0f57660926","tid":1104163,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:45:35.000Z","msg":"呢個就係你既人生"},{"pid":"b2cf45c3cbb21616e16f69d40412294213fc982f","tid":1104163,"uid":834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"641867d8e8292de45474471ea62ddf0f57660926","tid":1104163,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:45:35.000Z","msg":"呢個就係你既人生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:48:45.000Z","msg":"是咪即係垃圾人生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0c065fd160007e14bed47b688d8a61aab87d47","tid":1104163,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:49:14.000Z","msg":"開個post 打咁撚多字但係連份工係咩工都唔肯講"},{"pid":"1bf62da7012efa5eb1f82671ce310582784cf2ba","tid":1104163,"uid":834,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cc0c065fd160007e14bed47b688d8a61aab87d47","tid":1104163,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:49:14.000Z","msg":"開個post 打咁撚多字但係連份工係咩工都唔肯講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:50:22.000Z","msg":"工程打理狗"},{"pid":"a6f03ff326ceeefe8c9a0ad14938a3846c3379b7","tid":1104163,"uid":154570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"